name: Loveless
description:
Living in the NFT space for the first time. 
This piece was the final output of a projection mapping event where one of my pieces i had running was called "Loveless"
It was a generative video piece developed in Photoshop, After Effects, Cinema 4D and Resolume arena + multiple macbook pro's+projectors+MSFTkinect
This is a still frame output from the animation. 
This minting comes with a JPEG frame from the print that i did at the live event. 

LOVELESS LIVES ON. The full uncompressed photoshop file .psd link will be sent to you in a dropbox link one your collectable is transferred
